snippet.title: Socketeer - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Socketeer is an action-roguelike about hacking enemy robots to control their abilities and survive. 

Releasing on Steam, Xbox One and PS4 on August 21st, developed by Ice Beam and published by Alliance Digital Media.

socketeergame.com
